MySQL Connector Python requires python to be in the 
system’s PATH. Installation fails if it doesn’t find Python.

On Windows, If Python doesn’t exist in the system’s PATH, 
please manually add the directory containing python.exe 
yourself.

The Software used----<br>
Microsoft Windows10 as Operating System.
Python 3.7 as Front-end-Development environment.
MYSQL as Back-end Sever with Database for Testing
MS-Word 2022 for documentation
